---
title: Peanut-Hoisin Chicken Breasts Stir-Fry with Bok Choy and Peppers
description: Feeling nutty today? This stir-fry combines bold hoisin, zesty Moo Shu Spice Blend and earthy peanut butter to make a savoury sauce that coats juicy chicken, served with tender-crisp bok choy, sweet bell peppers  and buttery basmati rice.
